    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_2_0-54",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "0-54",
      "markText": "君子谋国，而小人谋身。谋国者，先忧天下；谋己者，先利自身。盖智者所图者远，所谋者深。惟其深远，方能顺天应人。",
      "totalCount": 1610,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_8_87-112",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "87-112",
      "markText": "事有不可拒者，勿拒。拖之缓之，消其势也，而后徐图。",
      "totalCount": 1536,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=87&rangeEnd=112",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=87&rangeEnd=112"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_4_0-33",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "0-33",
      "markText": "事上宜以诚，诚则无隙，故宁忤而不欺。不以小过而损大节，忠也，智也。",
      "totalCount": 1358,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_1_0-30",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "0-30",
      "markText": "月晕而风，础润而雨，人事虽殊，其理一也。惟善察者能见微知着。",
      "totalCount": 1243,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_10_285-314",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "285-314",
      "markText": "危在我，而施于人。故我危则人危，人不欲危，则必出我于厄难。",
      "totalCount": 1173,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=285&rangeEnd=314",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=285&rangeEnd=314"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_2_235-273",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "235-273",
      "markText": "所谋在势，势之变也，我强则敌弱，敌弱则我强。倾举国之兵而伐之，不如令其自伐。",
      "totalCount": 868,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=235&rangeEnd=273",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=235&rangeEnd=273"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_2_381-439",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "381-439",
      "markText": "人皆知金帛为贵，而不知更有远甚于金帛者。谋之不深，而行之不远。人取小，我取大；人视近，我视远。未雨绸缪，智者所为也。",
      "totalCount": 850,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=381&rangeEnd=439",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=381&rangeEnd=439"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_13_108-122",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "108-122",
      "markText": "智者借色伐人，愚者以色伐己。",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=108&rangeEnd=122",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=108&rangeEnd=122"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_3_237-252",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "237-252",
      "markText": "天下无不可用之材，唯在于所用。",
      "totalCount": 781,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=237&rangeEnd=252",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=237&rangeEnd=252"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_13_31-69",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "31-69",
      "markText": "美色置于前而心不动者，情必矫也。然好色不如尊贤。近色而远贤臣，智者所不为也。",
      "totalCount": 748,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=31&rangeEnd=69",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=31&rangeEnd=69"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_3_0-37",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "0-37",
      "markText": "为政之道，在于辨善恶，明赏罚。倘法明而令审，不卜而吉；劳养功贵，不祝而福。",
      "totalCount": 738,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_5_36-60",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "36-60",
      "markText": "人心有所叵测，知人机者，危矣。故知微者宜善藏之。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=36&rangeEnd=60",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=36&rangeEnd=60"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_2_279-343",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "279-343",
      "markText": "勇者搏之，不如智者谋之。以力取之，不如以计图之。攻而伐之，不如晓之以理，动之以情，诱之以利；或雷霆万钧，令人闻风丧胆，而后图之。",
      "totalCount": 690,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=279&rangeEnd=343",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=279&rangeEnd=343"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_1_100-116",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "100-116",
      "markText": "听其言而观其行，观其色而究其实。",
      "totalCount": 660,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=100&rangeEnd=116",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=100&rangeEnd=116"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_1_158-194",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "158-194",
      "markText": "察不明则奸佞生，奸佞生则贤人去，贤人去则国不举，国不举，必殆，殆则危矣。",
      "totalCount": 656,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=158&rangeEnd=194",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=158&rangeEnd=194"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_7_0-45",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "0-45",
      "markText": "城可摧而心不可折，帅可取而志不可夺。所难者惟在一心。攻其心，折其志，不战而屈之，谋之上也。",
      "totalCount": 644,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_9_0-29",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "0-29",
      "markText": "知其诡而不察，察而不示，导之以谬。攻子之盾，必持子之矛也。",
      "totalCount": 636,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "791538_4_206-260",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "206-260",
      "markText": "为上计，不以小惠，而以长策。小惠人人可为，长策非贤者不能为之。故事之以谀，不如进之以忠。助之喜，不如为之忧。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=791538&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=206&rangeEnd=260",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67f323305c13f267f1aff07?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=206&rangeEnd=260"
    },
    {
